290
01:13:19,358 --> 01:13:26,443
you express your love you use 
some things as presents

291
01:13:26,462 --> 01:13:30,144
that gives you joy.

292
01:14:00,769 --> 01:14:03,967
That doesn’t mean, by any chance,

293
01:14:04,057 --> 01:14:07,899
that you just give it to your Rakhi sister

294
01:14:07,934 --> 01:14:11,005
and not even to your wife, some present.

295
01:14:31,541 --> 01:14:36,247
So, the sap, as I always say, of compassion has to rise

296
01:14:36,273 --> 01:14:42,556
 in the plant, giving love to different parts,

297
01:14:42,612 --> 01:14:45,488
indifferent ways, whatever is required

298
01:14:45,515 --> 01:14:49,681
and that then evaporates

299
01:14:49,741 --> 01:14:53,391
or goes back resource.

300
01:15:21,703 --> 01:15:29,189
Attachment is the killer 
of pure love and compassion.

301
01:15:46,029 --> 01:15:51,007
So try to always find out, introspect.

302
01:15:51,020 --> 01:15:54,178
Are you attached  to your children, to your wife

303
