306
01:16:51,090 --> 01:16:55,512
You’ll be amazed, when you are absolutely detached

307
01:16:55,854 --> 01:17:04,825
and nourishing the different relationships 
that you have in a proper way,

308
01:17:05,325 --> 01:17:07,962
your joy is perfect.

